    {
      "id": 2,
      "component": "ArticleFeature",
      "locales": {
        "en": {
          "title": "{{A little bit}} about me..."
        },
        "de": {
          "title": "{{Ein bisschen}} über mich..."
        },
        "hr": {
          "title": "{{Malo}} o meni..."
        },
        "tr": {
          "title": "{{Biraz}} hakkında..."
        }
      },
      "settings": {
        "order_items_by": "id",
        "order_items_sort": "asc",
        "keepImageRow": true,
        "feature_layout_mode": "equal_split_fixed_vh_image",
        "feature_stack_order": "text_media",
        "feature_image_aspect_ratio": "1 / 1",
        "feature_image_mobile_aspect_ratio": "1 / 1",
        "feature_image_viewport_height": "30vw"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "img": "/images/private/LovroMusic2025.jpg",
          "imgAlt": "/images/contant/profil_dog.webp",
          "faIcon": "",
          "faIconColors": {
            "bg": "",
            "fill": "",
            "fillLight": ""
          },
          "locales": {
            "en": {
              "text": "{{Lovro Musić :}} Hi, I'm an aspiring hardware engineer in the beautiful Rhein-Main area. Growing up in a small village in the Bosnian mountains as a Croatian kid, I came to this land of possibilities in my early teens. I was fascinated by the advanced and diverse German engineering culture, something I had only dreamed of on TV. I started an apprenticeship with a Swiss enterprise as an Elektroniker für Automatisierungstechnik, which opened a Pandora's box and shaped me into the motivated and versatile tool I am today.<p>Now go explore what I have managed to present about me. I recommend starting with my <a href='#my-software'>Software &amp; Code</a> section, or my fun <a href='#my-art'>Web Art</a> section. If you just forgot the name of my language-learning website, visit <a href='https://lomuss33.github.io/GermanCro/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>GermanCro</a>.</p>"
            },
            "de": {
              "text": "{{Lovro Musić :}} Hallo, ich bin ein angehender Signal-Ingenieur in der schönen Rhein-Main-Region. Als kroatisches Kind, das in einem kleinen Dorf in den bosnischen Bergen aufwuchs, kam ich in meiner frühen Jugend in dieses Land der Möglichkeiten. Ich war fasziniert von der fortschrittlichen und vielfältigen deutschen Ingenieurkultur, von der ich nur im Fernsehen geträumt hatte. Ich begann eine Ausbildung bei einem Schweizer Unternehmen als Elektroniker für Automatisierungstechnik, die mir eine Pandora-Box öffnete und mich zu dem motivierten und vielseitigen Werkzeug machte, das ich heute bin.<p>Geh jetzt los und entdecke, was ich dir bisher ueber mich praesentieren konnte. Ich empfehle dir, mit meinem Bereich <a href='#my-software'>Software &amp; Code</a> zu starten, oder falls du einfach den Namen meiner Sprachlern-Website vergessen hast, besuche <a href='https://lomuss33.github.io/GermanCro/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>GermanCro</a>.</p>"
            },
            "hr": {
              "text": "{{Lovro Musić :}} Bok, ja sam budući inženjer singnalizacije u prelijepoj regiji Rhein-Main. Odrastajući u malom selu u bosanskim planinama kao hrvatski dječak, došao sam u ovu zemlju mogućnosti u svojim ranim tinejdžerskim godinama. Bio sam fasciniran naprednom i raznolikom njemačkom inženjerskom kulturom, o kojoj sam samo sanjao na televiziji. Počeo sam karijeru sa švicarskom firmom kao Elektroničar za automatizaciju, što mi je otvorilo Pandorinu kutiju i oblikovalo me u motivirani i raznovrstan alat kakav sam danas.<p>Sada idi istrazi i vidi sto sam ti trenutno uspio predstaviti o sebi. Preporucujem da krenes s mojim odjeljkom <a href='#my-software'>Software &amp; Code</a>, a ako si zaboravio kako se zove moja stranica za ucenje jezika, posjeti <a href='https://lomuss33.github.io/GermanCro/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>GermanCro</a>.</p>"
            },
            "tr": {
              "text": "{{Lovro Musić :}} Merhaba, ben güzel Rhein-Main bölgesinde bir hırslı donanım mühendisiyim. Bosna dağlarında küçük bir köyde Hırvat çocuğu olarak büyüyerek, ergenliğimin başında bu fırsatlar diyarına geldim. Gelişmiş ve çeşitli Alman mühendislik kültürü beni çok etkiledi; bunu yalnızca televizyonda hayal etmiştim. İleri otomasyon teknolojinleri üzerine uzmanlaşmak için bir İsviçre şirketinde staj yapmaya başladım; bu deneyim beni bugünkü motivasyonu yüksek ve çok yönlü bir alet haline getirdi.<p>Simdi git ve sana su ana kadar kendim hakkinda neleri gosterebildigimi kesfet. Baslangic icin <a href='#my-software'>Software &amp; Code</a> bolumumle baslamani oneririm; ya da dil ogrenme sitemin adini unuttuysan <a href='https://lomuss33.github.io/GermanCro/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>GermanCro</a>'yu ziyaret et.</p>"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
